Package: pygcmsqc
Type: Package
Title: Quality Control Pipeline for Pyrolysis GC-MS Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christian", "Freeman", email = "CDFREE2@emory.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A structured pipeline for processing, calibrating, and visualizing
    pyrolysis gas chromatography-mass spectrometry (py-GC-MS) data across multiple
    analytical batches. Implements weighted 1/x linear calibration with automated
    calibrator optimization, blank-subtracted concentration calculation in ug/g,
    LOD/LOQ estimation from blank distributions, and a full suite of QC,
    internal standard, calibration curve, and PCA diagnostic plots exported as
    publication-ready PDFs and styled Excel workbooks.
